data.description: Relax in your new pool and hot tub. Gather friends and family together in the outdoor kitchen and relax in the outdoor living area while you celebrate and make memories to last a lifetime.  Come inside and choose to gather in the downstairs living area or take in the newest release on your favorite streaming site in the private theater. Challenge friends to a game of cards or pool in the game room. Unwind in your downstairs primary suite at the end of a fun filled day. Solar Panels convey with the property, owned system, to enjoy lower electric bills all year long. This home has it all. The community amenities include 2 large pools, playground, and dog park, and is within walking distance to an elementary school. Make this your new home! 2023-10-15
